final_score = opinion_entropy × engagement_weight × freshness_factor

opinion_entropy = - [p_agree × ln(p_agree) + p_disagree × ln(p_disagree)]

p_agree = W_agree / W_polarized
p_disagree = W_disagree / W_polarized

W_agree = ∑ comment_weight of AGREE comments
W_neutral = ∑ comment_weight of NEUTRAL comments
W_disagree = ∑ comment_weight of DISAGREE comments

W_polarized = W_agree + W_disagree
W_total = W_agree + W_disagree + W_neutral

comment_weight = is_folded ? 0 : 1 + ln(like_count + 1) + 0.5 × ln(unique_reply_user_count + 1)


engagement_weight = 1 + ln(W_total + 1)

freshness_factor = max(0.3, 1 / (hour_count/24 + 1))

If W_polarized = 0, opinion_entropy = 0
If W_agree = 0 or W_disagree = 0, opinion_entropy = 0
If W_agree = W_disagree, opinion_entropy = ln(2) ≈ 0.693

A comment that is folded will not be counted towards opinion_entropy:
is_folded = 
True if report_scoreSPAM >= 2.0
True if report_scoreHARASSMENT >= 3.0
True if report_scoreOFFTOPIC >= 5.0
False otherwise 

Report system:
Each comment has report_scoreTYPE. A comment with report_scoreTYPE >= N (for that type) will be folded and not counted towards opinion_entropy. 

report_scoreTYPE = ∑ w_level for that TYPE

Each report can be assigned to one of three types.
SPAM 
HARASSMENT 
OFFTOPIC 

User role & w_level
Each user level contributes different w_level weight for calculating report_score 
New user (registered < 14 days) - 0.5
Official user (registered >= 14 days ) - 1.0
Reputable user (registered >= 14 days & receive likes from 100 different users) - 1.5
Administrator (through application) - 2.0 

Important features:
When user supplements their own opinion, they can only edit instead of replying to it. User can only reply to other users’ opinions

Abuse defense:
For same node, same user can only make 1 single reply for 5 minutes
Sensitive Word Filter
Manual review
